TaxReconciliationReport is a BusinessTask
    owned by tx

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            is report for PayablesManager, ApplicationAdministrator, FinancialsViewer, FinancialsProcessor, PayablesSpecialist, PayablesProcessor, ReceivablesManager
                report name is "Reconciliation"
                Description
                    List all invoices that were applied to a specific tax period.
                    The report subtotals by general ledger period or tax code.
            Reports
                TaxReconciliationReportReport

    Parameters
		TaxEntity
        Company                 is a GeneralLedgerCompany 
        BegYear                 is a TaxYear
        BegPeriod               is Numeric size 2 
        EndYear                 is a TaxYear
        EndPeriod               is Numeric size 2 
        ReportOption            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Detail  value is "1"
                Summary value is "2"
        ReportSeq               is Numeric size 1
            States
                GlAccount value is 1
                    default label is "GL Account"
                TaxCode   value is 2
        VatOnly                 is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"

    Parameter Rules
        Company
            required
        BegYear
            required
        BegPeriod
            required
        ReportOption
        	initial value is "1"
            default to "1"
        ReportSeq
        	initial value is "1"
            default to 1
        VatOnly
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        TaxEntity
        	initial value is Company.AccountingEntity
            default to Company.AccountingEntity

    Actions
        TaxReconciliationReport is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
